name: Not yet another farmer game
description:
In "Not yet another farmer game" you play as farmer, collecting vegetables (and dope :)) and must seed the holes and harvest the stuff.

It is a bit of a "chill" game but also a bit of stress of arcade.

In every Level you have a required amount of vegetables that you need to harvest (but you can harvest more to gain more score).

All Assets were made by me.
